content:
Open question Is these a need for a better file format for our data?
Ideally a file format should be self-describing. Some existing data file formats for SIMS include&hellip;
Spectra-focussed JCAMP-DX SPC VAMAS (ISO 14976:1998 with ISO 22048:2004) Hyperspectral image-focussed imzML Other formats that could be explored include NetCDF HDF5 Apache Arrow Apache Parquet Apache Feather Open questions Which software packages can write these formats? Which software packages can read these formats?
